column2: SELECT COUNT (*) FROM GalSpecLine AS gs JOIN SpecPhoto AS sp ON sp.specobjid = gs.specobjid JOIN dbo.fGetNearbySpecObjEq (#, #, #) AS GN ON GN.specobjID = gs.specobjid JOIN Galaxy as gal ON gal.specobjId = gs.specobjid JOIN PhotoObjAll as p ON p.specObjId = gs.specobjID WHERE h_alpha_eqw between # and # and oii_#_eqw between # and #
